Content: You pull the harness over your head,|push the ball in and strap the buckles.
You stuff the wadding in your mouth, then tie|more cloths over your mouth and around your head.
You pull a band of duct tape and|apply it firmly over your mouth.
Are you sure you want to lock the|belt on yourself?  Click again to do so.
You take a deep breath and close the belt|on yourself.  It locks with a loud "click".
You kneel down to get your ankles in their manacles.|Once locked on you secure your wrists behind you.
After a while Jenna enters the room|and walks over to you.
